question: Tī tsū-liau lāi-bīn, ū 3 ê ya kó͘-sū í-siōng ê tō-ián, tō-ián ê tiān-iáⁿ sī chin-koân ê chi̍t ê? O̍h sī tō-ián ê tiān-iáⁿ ūi-tio̍h ê chha-chí siōng-koân?
2009 nî sî-kan hō͘ chhut-hiān ê só͘-ū iáⁿ-phîⁿ ê chóng koan-chiòng chhù bān jī-bīn sī créme?
Siaⁿ-tiâu tńg lâi chin chē ê phiah phiah ê chha̍h-chha̍h ê chha̍h ê jîn, chiah lâi lia̍t chhut chha̍h ê jîn ê tùi-chhiùⁿ ê jîn ê phiah chha̍h ê phiah ê phiah ê phiah ê chha̍h ê phiah ê jîn.
2008 nî 10 goe̍h ê koan-chiòng chha̍h-chha̍p thû, cháiⁿ ū chē-chē chha̍h-chha̍p thû?
answer: 2008 nî 10 goe̍h ê sî-chūn, koan-chiòng chha̍h-chha̍p thû sī ū chi̍t-ê chiâu-ti̍t ê hā-chhiúⁿ. I tī 10 goe̍h 9 hō ê "Business Ethics" khai-sí sī 8.99 pah-bān, sak kàu 10 goe̍h 16 hō ê "Baby Shower" sī 8.07 pah-bān, chiap-jīm sak kàu 10 goe̍h 23 hō ê "Crime Aid" sī 7.74 pah-bān, liáu-āu tī goe̍h-té ê 10 goe̍h 30 hō ū chi̍t-ê hāu-li̍p ê seng-koân, tit kàu 9.32 pah-bān ê "Employee Transfer", chiah phah-phòaⁿ goe̍h-té ê hā-chhiúⁿ ê khó͘-sè.

question: M̄-tōa-liōng chiâⁿ-chú Mindy Kaling siá ê chhut-liàn-phín, i ê koan-chiòng chhāi 8.500 bān khah kē ê tit-chhut sī ūi-tiāⁿ ê muî-chi̍t ê hō-miâ? (M̄-tōa-liōng chiâⁿ-chú Mindy Kaling siá ê chhut-liàn-phín, i ê koan-chiòng chhāi 8.500 bān khah kē ê tit-chhut sī ūi-tiāⁿ ê muî-chi̍t ê hō-miâ?)
Ēng-tó͘ "Stress Relief" chi̍t chi̍p, chiū án-choánn chē pí-lu̍t chiàm liáu chit kuí kiat chhò͘ (chham-khó chē-piáⁿ) ê chóng-thé koan-chiòng chha̍p-sò͘?
Juah Randall Einhorn chiong--ê oá--lâng ê téng-hō--ê 15% ê kóaⁿ lâi kóaⁿ ê tiān-sī oá--ê bô͘? I ê oá--lâng ê chòe-chóng tiān-sī oá--ê kiám-luí ū thè kiáⁿ siáⁿ-chē?
Tse ū-khó-lêng ài kóng-sū ê ēng-phîng-bé kah i kó-thok ê ji̍t-kî chi-kan ū chi̍t-ê tiāu-khak ê koan-hē bô? Kái-soeh lí ê goân-in.
answer: Bô, bô chi̍t-ê chin tiāu-khak ê koan-hē. Kó-thok ê ēng-phîng-bé tùi-tī tāi-liōng sī sòa-khì ê, mā kah i phoat-iāⁿ ê sòa-lia̍t ū ha̍h, m̄-koh ū chē-ê lē-gōa. Tùi-jū, "Frame Toby" (kó-thok ê ēng-phîng-bé 5008) tī 2008 nî 11 goe̍h 20 ji̍t phoat-iāⁿ, che sī tī "Business Trip" (kó-thok ê ēng-phîng-bé 5009) tī 2008 nî 11 goe̍h 13 ji̍t phoat-iāⁿ ê āu-piah. Che tùi-tī chè-chok ê sòa-lia̍t bô-hoat-tō͘ tō chiap chin chòe-tōi ê chha-pia̍t.

question: Na-chheng phoe-chhut ê miâ-jī sī kāng chi̍t ê chiat-bo̍k ê pêng-kin tōa-chúi phiah-tùi lâi kóng, sī chin keh-tah ê, koh ū i thong-kòe 14.68 bān ê chi̍t ê-bān-ê tōa-chúi hō͘-siong pí ūi?
Eh keh bo liao liam-chhit si-liau ê chu tiâu ū-tāi su-liāu? In-ū i ū chha-jit hû-hō "/" ê sî-chūn, koh ū in ê chu tiâu ê miâ-jī? (Tiâu-mûi: "No. in series", "" Weight Loss "‡", "" Stress Relief "‡")

2008 nî ê Kūng-chok Kūi (The Office) téng-sî, tī Ài-gí-lâi-á (Australia) ê tē-khu ê àn-chiáⁿ-chha̍h (viewership) sī siáⁿ-mih? (Tī phoe-chhat bô siáⁿ-mih tē-khu ê chu-liāu, chia̍h-chòe sī Bí-kok ê chu-liāu)
